$(document).ready(function() {
  // Simple solution for DT in tabs and details elements
  
  // Function to reinitialize DataTables
  function reinitializeDataTables() {
    setTimeout(function() {
      $('.dataTables_wrapper').each(function() {
        var table = $(this).find('table').DataTable();
        if (table) {
          try {
            table.columns.adjust();
            table.responsive.recalc();
          } catch(e) {
            // Ignore errors
          }
        }
      });
    }, 150);
  }
  
  // Handle Bootstrap tab events
  $(document).on('shown.bs.tab', 'a[data-toggle="tab"], button[data-bs-toggle="tab"]', function (e) {
    reinitializeDataTables();
  });
  
  // Handle details toggle events
  $(document).on('toggle', 'details', function(e) {
    if (this.open) {
      reinitializeDataTables();
    }
  });
  
  // Handle clicks on summary elements
  $(document).on('click', 'summary', function() {
    setTimeout(reinitializeDataTables, 200);
  });
  
  // Tab click handlers
  $(document).on('click', '.nav-tabs a, .nav-pills a', function() {
    setTimeout(reinitializeDataTables, 250);
  });
  
  // Initial setup
  setTimeout(reinitializeDataTables, 500);
  setTimeout(reinitializeDataTables, 1500); // Extra delay for safety
  
  // Window resize
  $(window).on('resize', function() {
    setTimeout(reinitializeDataTables, 100);
  });
});
